      <p>Founded in 2015, Floatie Kings was inspired by our love of summer and a dream of spreading California pool party culture across the world. Today, our luxury, custom-designed <a href="javascript:void(0)">pool floats</a> can be spotted at the hottest pool parties and beaches in Ibiza, Miami, Rio, Bali and wherever summer stories are made.</p>
